<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>ema612_08_ih_0002</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
    <script src="../../common_practice/common/js/solve_area_act.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/common/css/app.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/css/ema612_08.css" />
  </head>

  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema612_08_ih_0002">
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-head="2">
          <span class="label_bogi ty2" lang="y">보기</span>
          <span lang="y">에서 알맞은 말을</span>
          <span class="empty_box nemo"></span></span>
          <span lang="y">안에 써넣으세요.</span>
        </h2>
      </section>

      <section class="contents">
        <div class="question_box justify_center align_cener">
          <div class="text_area">
            <span class="label_bogi ty2">보기</span>
            <p lang="y">꼭짓점</p>
            <p lang="y">모서리</p>
            <p lang="y">각뿔의 꼭짓점</p>
            <p lang="y">높이</p>
          </div>
          <div class="img_area">
            <img src="./../../common_practice/img/EMA612_08_IH/0002_01.png" alt="" />
            <div class="input_wrap input1">
              <math-field data-answer-single="모서리" text-align="center"></math-field>
            </div>
            <div class="input_wrap input2">
              <math-field data-answer-single="꼭짓점" text-align="center"></math-field>
            </div>
            <div class="input_wrap input3">
              <math-field data-answer-single="각뿔의 꼭짓점" text-align="center"></math-field>
            </div>
            <div class="input_wrap input4">
              <math-field data-answer-single="높이" text-align="center"></math-field>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- 해설 -->
        <div class="solve_area">
          <div class="inner_solve">
            <div class="flex">
              <strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
              <div class="conts_solve">
                <p lang="y">각뿔에서 면과 면이 만나는 선분을 모서리, 모서리와 모서리가 만나는 점을 꼭짓점이라고 합니다. 꼭짓점 중에서도 옆면이 모두 만나는 점을 각뿔의 꼭짓점, 각뿔의 꼭짓점과 밑면 사이의 거리를 높이라고 합니다.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="buttons_solve"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
